Who's ready for the big #UFC fight this weekend with TJ Dillashaw!? We shot this brand entertainment with Lucia Entertainment and TJ  a few weeks ago. Amazing turn around Lucia! The drone/aerial graphics at about :32 of the plans going to a real shot of the home are beautiful. We chose a MP2 over a Inspire 2 to fly up close to people working on the roof. ESP and TJ were really class acts. GO TJ!

Wow, I am extremely proud to finally catch this project I worked on last year with all3media for Showtime! What a fabulously well produced documentary.  I'm flattered so many of my shots were used for the final cut. 
I have to mention how humbling and interesting it was to sit and talk with the officers that went through this ordeal and protected the people of San Bernadino with their lives. SB is a dangerous place every day, and that day they really showed how much they are willing to give.

If you're in Lone Tree, Colorado area, stop by the official #DJI #Colorado store and check out the #MavMount, now for sale in store!

We're proud and excited to be a part of a flagship DJi store!

The MAVMOUNT is a high quality mounting system that allows use of a tablet for the DJI Mavic drone. Now you can use an Ipad mini, Nvidia Shield tablet, or any other compatible tablet with your Mavic Drone. Includes MADE IN THE USA CNC machined and anodized plate, machined large fully adjustable ball-head, and spring loaded tablet holder. Everything you need for easy use. NO expensive extra parts to buy or cannibalize from other drones!

Doing some shakedown flights at my local park after a long road trip from texas to NYC with Gordon Ramseys new show. After a lot of shooting, travel/driving/flights, I like to recalibrate and update everything if needed.

Everything is gunmetal today. inspire 2 with Olympus 45mm lens and controller in gunmetal, and of course a MavMount and Mavic in gunmetal grey as well.

On film shoots where we don't want to kill a battery on the inspire 2, maybe because we're in the middle of the desert, the mavic is a great tool. Tons of time in the air for checking out shots, and then bam, put the big Bird up for the main shoot. For this wet use the mavmount, a professional solution to using a full sized tablet for our display.
